div.label: English
div.div: Flag of Somaliland (1991-1996). The flag founder and designer was Gen. Mohamoud Suleiman Harun

table.style: border:2px solid #D3D3D3; width:100%; background-color:#F8F8F8; text-align:center; direction:ltr;

tr.td: It is easy to put a border around this flag image:

td.div: العربية: علم أرض الصومال بين عامي ١٩٩١ (١٤١١) و ١٩٩٦ (١٤١٧)
English: Flag of Somaliland between 1991 and 1996
Soomaaliga: Calanka Somaliland oo u dhexeeya 1991 (1411) iyo 1996 (1417)

tr.td: It is from the xrmap flag collection, specifically "somaliland.svg" in flags-2.6-src.tar.bz2.
The README file in flags-2.6-src.tar.bz2 says of the SVG flags "We release them in the public domain".
